(180, 15, 'es_builder_private', '			<article data-ix=\"article-15126754343141849\" data-clickable=\"true\" class=\"\"><div class=\"cols\" data-ix=\"row-151267544602984178\" data-clickable=\"true\"><div class=\"col-xsmall-8\" data-ix=\"column-151267545108345954\" data-clickable=\"true\">col-xsmall-8 <div class=\"editable_item no-margins\" data-ix=\"column-151267545108345954_content\"><p>License</p><input name=\"column-content-editor\" id=\"column-content-editor\" type=\"text\" data-ix=\"column-151267545108345954_hidden\" hidden=\"hidden\" value=\"<h2>License</h2><p>The enedScroll is subject to the license selected when purchasing the product.</p><p><a class=&quot;inline&quot; href=&quot;https://codecanyon.net/licenses/standard&quot;>Read more about Envato licenses</a>&nbsp;</p><p><a class=&quot;inline&quot; href=&quot;https://codecanyon.net/licenses/faq&quot;>FAQ Envato licenses</a></p>\"></div></div></div></article><article data-ix=\"article-15126754421368502\" data-clickable=\"true\" class=\"\"><div class=\"cols\" data-ix=\"row-151267549484873180\" data-clickable=\"true\"><div class=\"col-xsmall-8\" data-ix=\"column-151267549764635399\" data-clickable=\"true\">col-xsmall-8 <div class=\"editable_item no-margins\" data-ix=\"column-151267549764635399_content\"><p>Installing</p><input name=\"column-content-editor\" id=\"column-content-editor\" type=\"text\" data-ix=\"column-151267549764635399_hidden\" hidden=\"hidden\" value=\"<h2>Installing</h2><p>To get started with enedScroll you need jQuery version &amp;lt; 1.x.x and enedScroll files.</p><p>Before [markup]&amp;lt;/body&amp;gt;[/markup] tag you should include once of enedScroll version, normall or minifed. You can use code below.</p><p>[code]&amp;lt;script src=&quot;enedScroll.min.js&quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;[/code]</p>\"></div></div></div></article><article data-ix=\"article-151267544256180038\" data-clickable=\"true\" class=\"\"><div class=\"cols\" data-ix=\"row-151267555546249998\" data-clickable=\"true\"><div class=\"col-xsmall-8\" data-ix=\"column-151267555794659229\" data-clickable=\"true\">col-xsmall-8 <div class=\"editable_item no-margins\" data-ix=\"column-151267555794659229_content\"><p>Trigger</p><input name=\"column-content-editor\" id=\"column-content-editor\" type=\"text\" data-ix=\"column-151267555794659229_hidden\" hidden=\"hidden\" value=\"<h2 class=&quot;title&quot;>Trigger</h2><p>This is a magic wand with which you can determine when to call your scene. For a more detailed description of Trigger you will find it here <em><strong>{{ a &amp;gt; trigger - add element }}</strong></em>.</p>\"></div></div></div></article><article data-ix=\"article-151267544297661342\" data-clickable=\"true\" class=\"\"><div class=\"cols\" data-ix=\"row-151267562192048055\" data-clickable=\"true\"><div class=\"col-xsmall-8\" data-ix=\"column-151267562499452981\" data-clickable=\"true\">col-xsmall-8 <div class=\"editable_item no-margins\" data-ix=\"column-151267562499452981_content\"><p>Selectors</p><input name=\"column-content-editor\" id=\"column-content-editor\" type=\"text\" data-ix=\"column-151267562499452981_hidden\" hidden=\"hidden\" value=\"<h2 class=&quot;title&quot;>Selectors</h2><p>Selectors as trigger can determine moment to call your event.</p><p>Exists 2 selectors, top and bottom. Specifies a moment of a function call is based on the element that was assigned to the scene as a target.</p>\"></div></div></div></article><article data-ix=\"article-151267544332738019\" data-clickable=\"true\" class=\"\"><div class=\"cols\" data-ix=\"row-151267565549745184\" data-clickable=\"true\"><div class=\"col-xsmall-8 checked\" data-ix=\"column-151267565826783913\" data-clickable=\"true\">col-xsmall-8 <div class=\"editable_item no-margins\" data-ix=\"column-151267565826783913_content\"><p>Scene</p><input name=\"column-content-editor\" id=\"column-content-editor\" type=\"text\" data-ix=\"column-151267565826783913_hidden\" hidden=\"hidden\" value=\"<h2 class=&quot;title&quot;